data.meta_description: Dec 24, 2016 - Lais Ribeiro (born in Teresina, Piau√≠, 1992) is a Brazilian model. In 2009, she started modelling locally & shortly after walked the major international catwalks for Chanel, Louis Vuitton, Gucci, Dolce & Gabbana, Versace, & Marc Jacobs. During Brazil fashion week in 2011, she was the most booked runway model, booking 63 shows. She has been in American Vogue & Vogue Italia, & in ads for Ralph Lauren, Christian Dior, Tom Ford, & Victoria's Secret. See more ideas about lais ribeiro, brazilian models, model.
